<body style="background-image: url(https://images.pexels.com/photos/533923/pexels-photo-533923.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940); background-repeat:no-repeat; background-size:cover; background-position:center;">
<!-- https://images.pexels.com/photos/662994/pexels-photo-662994.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&dpr=2&h=650&w=940-->
<br>

<div class="container" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 150px">
      <div class="card" style="width: 60rem; display: inline-block;">
         <div class="card-body">
         <p class="card-text">
          <h1 style="font-size: 100px; font-weight:500"><%=@hostel.name%></h1>
          <h2> L'un de nos hôtels préférés ! </h2>
         </p>

<div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide carousel-fade" data-ride="carousel" style="width: 600px; height:600px;margin-top: 50px; display: inline-block;">
  <ol class="carousel-indicators">
    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
    <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
  </ol>
  <div class="carousel-inner">
    <div class="carousel-item active">
      <img class="d-block w-100"   src="https://hostelkite.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/guesthouse01.jpg" alt="First slide">
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://hostelkite.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/guesthouse02.jpg" alt="Second slide">
    </div>
    <div class="carousel-item">
      <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://hostelkite.s3.eu-west-3.amazonaws.com/guesthouse03.jpeg" alt="Third slide">
    </div>
  </div>

  <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
    <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
  </a>
  <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
    <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
  </a>
</div>
</div>



<div class="row mx-auto" style="margin-top: 30px; text-align:center; justify-content:center; align-items:center; ">
  <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-lg-0 mb-5">
    <div class="card" style="width: 20rem; margin-left: -120px;">
      <div class="card-body">
      <h4 class="card-title" style="color: #51bcda">Description</h4>
      <br>
      <p> Une magnifique auberge située à moins de 200 mètres de la plage. Vous pourrez profiter d'un grand jardin, pour vous détendre sous les palmiers après une longue journée de kite-surf.

      </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6 mb-lg-0 mb-5">
    <div class="card" style="width: 20rem">
      <div class="card-body">
      <h4 class="card-title" style="color: #51bcda">Réservation</h4>
      <br>
      <p class="card-text" style="font-style: italic;">Localisation: <%=@hostel.address %>, <%=@hostel.zip_code%> <%=@hostel.city %>
      <p class="card-text" style="font-style: italic;">
      <i class="nc-alert-circle-i"></i>

      Nombre de lits disponibles: <%=@hostel.bed_number%>  </p>

      </p>
      <p class="card-text" style="font-style: italic;">
      <i class="nc-money-coins"></i>
      Prix d'un lit /nuit :<%=@hostel.price%> </p>

      </p>

      </div>

    </div>




</div>

</div>
<div class="container" style="margin-bottom: 20px"> 
 <a href="<%=new_booking_path(hostels_id:@hostel.id)%>" class="btn ">Je réserve!</a>
 <a href="<%= root_path %>" class="btn ">Retour à l'accueil</a>
</div>

  </div>
</div>


</body>
